definitions.definition: A person who lives in a forest .
Any of various species of kangaroo that inhabit bushland , especially the eastern grey kangaroo .
A moth in the family Zygaenidae .
Any of various nymphalid butterflies of the genus Lethe . Other members of this genus are called tree browns and wood browns .

main_definition: ( forestry ) A person who practices forestry .
